hello.sh : A simple hello world
helloArgs.sh : A simple hello with an user input
loop.sh : Looping using for & while loops
arrays.sh : Creating & manipulating arrays
searchFileWord.sh : Searches word recursively in the .sh files of directory
searchFileWordPrint.sh : Searches word recursively in the .sh files of directory & prints the line of occurance
searchFiles.sh : Finds all .sh files upto input maxDepth
functions.sh : Function & there invocation using case statement based on user input
alias.sh: Alias creator. Takes two input arguments i)alias name ii)alias location

TestData for file search/manipulation:
files : List of files
moreFiles : List of more files

